1598155200.title: CNN Newsroom
1598155200.descr: CNN Newroom provides the most up to date news as it breaks and is the longest running show on the channel, airing twice a day Monday to Friday and throughout the day over the weekends. CNN was founding in 1980 by American media proprietor Ted Turner as a 24 hour cable news channel and has since won multiple media awards.

1598176800.title: Quest's World of Wonder
1598176800.descr: Join our host, Richard Quest, as he takes us on a journey of discovery to some of the most iconic cities on the planet. Richard encounters many of the influential local inhabitants and delves into the heritage and culture of each city to reveal what makes them unique and fascinating. The first series sees Richard travel around the globe to visit Washington D.C., Panama City, Nairobi, London, Berlin and Istanbul.

1598184000.title: Inside Politics
1598184000.descr: Inside Politics is a political talk show, broadcast on CNN and anchored by CNN Chief National Correspondent John King. It features the most important political stories presented by a panel of well-sourced reporters. John King is an experienced reporter who covers the White House, Congress and the campaign trail, and interviews presidents, politicians and voters.

1598187600.title: U.S. State of the Union Address
1598187600.descr: Jake Tapper brings together major news makers, analysts and experts to tackle pressing domestic issues and diplomacy on the global stage.

1598191200.title: Fareed Zakaria GPS
1598191200.descr: Fareed Zakaria GPS is a weekly public affairs show hosted by an American journalist, political scientist, and author Fareed Zakaria. The "GPS" in the show's title stands for "Global Public Square," a reference to the show's focus on international issues and foreign affairs.

1598194800.title: Reliable Sources
1598194800.descr: Reliable Sources is a CNN Sunday morning talk show focused on analysis of the American news media, hosted by Brian Stelter. The media world is thoroughly examined and the news stories of the previous week are covered. The talk show highlights news about news and tells story behind the story, and features one-on-one interviews with journalists taking part in a news event.
